            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Hello @EmilieDel,\r\n\r\nAccording to the doc, it seems possible to create a full-text index at table creation.\r\n\r\nMaybe it could make things even simpler doing so?\r\n\r\nThe syntax would be:\r\n\r\n```\r\nCREATE TABLE table (\r\n    ...\r\n    column TEXT,\r\n    FULLTEXT (column)\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\nSource: https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/fulltext-natural-language.html.",
